<div class="tip_number">TIP 19</div>
<div class="tip_contents">
            When your line of vision becomes narrowed or you experience any defect in your field of vision, it may be an important symptom of a pituitary gland tumor, a brain tumor, a stroke, an injury to the retina of the eye, or advanced glaucoma.
        </div>

</div>
